sequenceDiagram
    participant B as "Browser (React SPA)"
    participant API as ".NET 10 API (App Service)"
    participant MSID as "Microsoft Identity"
    participant KV as "Key Vault (PoShared)"
    participant DB as "SQLite (/home/data)"
    participant HUB as "SignalR Hub"
    Note over API,KV: API Startup — resolve secrets via Managed Identity
    API->>KV: GetSecret(MicrosoftAuth--ClientId)
    API->>KV: GetSecret(MicrosoftAuth--ApiClientId)
    API->>KV: GetSecret(ApplicationInsights--ConnectionString)
    KV-->>API: Secrets injected into IConfiguration
    Note over B,MSID: Authentication Flow (Microsoft OAuth2 — MSAL popup)
    B->>MSID: GET /authorize (MSAL popup redirect)
    MSID-->>B: authorization_code returned
    B->>MSID: POST /token (code + PKCE exchange)
    MSID-->>B: JWT access_token + id_token (12h TTL)
    B->>API: GET /api/auth/me  [Authorization: Bearer JWT]
    API->>MSID: Validate JWT (signature, audience, issuer)
    MSID-->>API: Claims verified
    API-->>B: 200 {userId, displayName, email}
    Note over B,DB: Game Stats — Create / Update / Read
    B->>API: PUT /api/tictactoe/players/{name}/stats  [Bearer]
    API->>DB: UPSERT PlayerStats (Game=tictactoe, PlayerName, StatsJson)
    DB-->>API: OK
    API-->>B: 200 updated stats
    B->>API: GET /api/tictactoe/statistics/leaderboard?limit=10
    API->>DB: SELECT Game, PlayerName, StatsJson ORDER BY WinRate DESC LIMIT 10
    DB-->>API: top 10 rows
    API-->>B: [{name, winRate, totalGames, totalWins}]
    Note over B,HUB: High Scores (Snake / PoDropSquare)
    B->>API: POST /api/snake/highscores  {initials, score, duration, length, food}
    API->>DB: INSERT SnakeHighScores
    DB-->>API: OK
    API-->>B: 201 saved entry
    B->>API: GET /api/snake/highscores?count=10
    DB-->>API: top 10 by Score DESC
    API-->>B: [{initials, score, date, gameDuration}]
    Note over B,HUB: Multiplayer — Lobby + Real-time SignalR
    B->>API: POST /api/multiplayer/queue  {gameKey: "tictactoe"}  [Bearer]
    API-->>B: {matchId, status: "waiting"}
    B->>HUB: WS /api/hubs/lobby?access_token=JWT
    HUB-->>B: LobbyUpdated {players, host, isStarting}
    B->>HUB: StartGame("tictactoe")  [host only]
    HUB-->>B: GameStarting {gameKey}  [broadcast all]
    B->>HUB: WS /api/hubs/multiplayer?access_token=JWT
    HUB-->>B: Connected — JoinGroup(matchId)
    B->>HUB: SendRealtimeInput(matchId, {col: 2, row: 1})
    HUB-->>B: RealtimeInput {fromUserId, fromDisplayName, payload, sentAt}
